et Simpson]]\n|18\u201319 April 2007\n|\n|{{flagicon|MRI}} [[R\u00e9duit (Mauritius)|R\u00e9duit]], Mauritius\n|\n|-\n|colspan=5| ''(100 m)'', ''(discus)'', ''(pole vault)'', ''(javelin)'', ''(400 m)'' / ''(100 m hurdles)'', ''(long jump)'', ''(shot put)'', ''(high jump)'', ''(1500 m)''\n|\n|-\n|[[20 kilometres race walk|20 km walk]] (road)\n|1:55:42 *\n|[[Jacqueline Ado Bludo]]\n|29 April 2006\n|\n|{{flagicon|GHA}} [[Cape Coast]], Ghana\n|\n|-\n|[[50 kilometres race walk|50 km walk]] (road)\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[4 \u00d7 100 metres relay|4 \u00d7 100 m relay]]\n|42.67\n|{{flagu|Ghana}}<br>[[Flings Owusu-Agyapong]]<br>[[Gemma Acheampong]]<br>[[Beatrice Gyaman]]<br>[[Janet Amponsah]]\n|8 July 2016\n|Soga-Nana Memorial\n|{{flagicon|GHA}} [[Cape Coast]], Ghana\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Soga-Nana Memorial, Cape Coast (Ghana) 8/07/2016|url=http://www.africathle.com/2016/07/08/soga-nana-memorial-cape-coast-ghana-8072016/|publisher=africathle.com|date=8 July 2016|accessdate=12 July 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[4 \u00d7 400 metres relay|4 \u00d7 400 m relay]]\n|3:35.55\n|{{flagu|Ghana}}<br>[[Helena Opoku]]<br>[[Grace Bakari]]<br>[[Georgina Aidoo]]<br>[[Hannah Afriyie]]\n|27 July 1978\n|[[Athletics at the 1978 All-Africa Games|All-Africa Games]]\n|{{flagicon|ALG}} [[Algiers]], Algeria\n|\n|}\n\n==Indoor==\n\n===Men===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:95%; width: 95%;\"\n|-\n!Event\n!Record\n!Athlete\n!Date\n!Meet\n!Place\n!Ref\n|-\n|[[50 metres|50 m]]\n|5.62+\n|[[Eric Nkansah]]\n|21 February 1999\n|[[Meeting Pas de Calais]]\n|{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Li\u00e9vin]], France\n|\n|-\n|[[55 metres|55 m]]\n|6.02 A\n|[[Leonard Myles-Mills]]\n|22 February 1997\n|\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Colorado Springs, Colorado|Colorado Springs]], United States\n|\n|-\n|[[60 metres|60 m]]\n|6.45 A\n|[[Leonard Myles-Mills]]\n|20 February 1999\n|\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Colorado Springs, Colorado|Colorado Springs]], United States\n|\n|-\n|rowspan=4|[[200 metres|200 m]]\n|20.80\n|[[Joseph Amoah (sprinter)|Jos