lan]]\n|{{flagicon|SWE}} [[Stockholm]], Sweden\n|\n|-\n|[[Triple jump]]\n|16.91 m\n|[[Andrew Owusu]]\n|24 January 1998\n|\n|{{flagicon|USA}}  [[Lincoln, Nebraska|Lincoln]], United States\n|\n|-\n|[[Shot put]]\n|17.81 m\n|[[Kwabena Keene]]\n|27 February 2010\n|ACC Championships\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Blacksburg, Virginia|Blacksburg]], United States\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Shot Put Results|url=http://www.directathletics.com/results/track/14099_965486.html?athlete_hnd=2231745|publisher=directathletics.com|date=27 February 2010|accessdate=1 November 2011}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[Heptathlon]]\n|5465 pts\n|[[Atsu Nyamadi]]\n|24\u201325 February 2016\n|Conference USA Championships\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Birmingham, Alabama|Birmingham]], United States\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Heptathlon Results|url=https://www.tfrrs.org/results/42504_2674749.html?athlete_hnd=5093574|publisher=tfrrs.org|date=25 February 2016|accessdate=13 September 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n|colspan=5|7.10 ''(60 m)'', 7.13 m ''(long jump)'', 13.27 m ''(shot put)'', 2.00 m ''(high jump)'' / 8.50 ''(60 m hurdles)'', 4.00 m ''(pole vault)'', 2:45.93 ''(1000 m)''\n|\n|-\n|[[5000 metres race walk|5000 m walk]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[4 \u00d7 400 metres relay|4 \u00d7 400 m relay]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|}\n\n===Women===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:95%; width: 95%;\"\n|-\n!Event\n!Record\n!Athlete\n!Date\n!Meet\n!Place\n!Ref\n|-\n|[[55 metres|55 m]]\n|7.03\n|[[Gemma Acheampong]]\n|5 February 2016\n|Crimson Elite\n|[[Cambridge, Massachusetts|Cambridge]], United States\n|<ref>{{cite news|title=55m Dash Results|url=https://www.directathletics.com/results/track/41912_2646768.html?athlete_hnd=4188012|publisher=directathletics.com|date=5 February 2016|accessdate=13 September 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=4|[[60 metres|60 m]]\n|rowspan=3|7.18\n|[[Vida Anim]]\n|27 February 2004\n|\n|[[Chemnitz]], Germany\n|\n|-\n|[[Flings Owusu-Agyapong]]\n|16 January 2015\n|Gotham Cup\n|[[New York City]], United States\n|<ref>{{cite web|t