al Tyson Track Center|Fayetteville]], United States\n|\n|-\n|[[Weight throw]]\n|19.59 m\n|[[Emelda Malm-Annan]]\n|11 December 2015\n|University of Wyoming Power Meet\n|[[Laramie, Wyoming|Laramine]], United States\n|<ref>{{cite news|title=Weight Throw Results|url=https://www.tfrrs.org/results/42202_2595418.html?athlete_hnd=5584168|publisher=tfrrs.org|date=11 December 2015|accessdate=13 September 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[Women's pentathlon|Pentathlon]]\n|3742 pts\n|[[Elizabeth Dadzie]]\n|24 February 2016\n|Conference USA Championships\n|[[Birmingham, Alabama|Birmingham]], United States\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Pentathlon Results|url=https://www.tfrrs.org/results/42504_2674781.html?athlete_hnd=5580473|publisher=tfrrs.org|date=24 February 2016|accessdate=13 September 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n|colspan=5|8.72 ''(60 m hurdles)'', 1.57 m ''(high jump)'', 10.50 m ''(shot put)'', 5.99 m ''(long jump)'', 2:32.35 ''(800 m)''\n|\n|-\n|[[3000 metres race walk|3000 m walk]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[4 \u00d7 400 metres relay|4 \u00d7 400 m relay]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|}\n\n==References==\n;General\n*[http://www.ghaathletics.com/?p=basketball&id=226 Ghanaian Records] <small>''25 January 2018 updated''</small>\n;Specific\n{{Reflist|2}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.ghaathletics.com/ GAA web site]\n\n{{Records in athletics}}\n{{National records in athletics}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ghanaian records in athletics}}\n[[Category:National records in athletics (track and field)]]\n[[Category:Ghana sport-related lists|Athletics records]]\n[[Category:Athletics in Ghana| Records]]\n", "name_user": "Rodw", "label": "safe", "comment": "Disambiguating links toCollege Station(link changed toCollege Station, Texas) usingDisamAssist.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Ghanaian_records_in_athletics"}
